channel.description:
Hey guys I finally released a new track, and it would be awesome if any of you wanted to check it out! I'm trying to improve at my tracks with vocals, so any feedback would be greatly appreciated. :)
https://soundcloud.com/user-andrewadams/when-i-need-you-the-most
Hope you guys have/are having a great summer!
-- Andrew
